      "description": "Sunshine (#faa31b) is a PRIMARY tier color used broadly (gradients, chart figure emphasis, campaign headline colorway, CTA fallback), but the only token holding this hex is narrowly IDed 'background_gradient_cta_fallback' though keyed as 'color.primary.sunshine'. No generic reusable Sunshine primitive exists, unlike Brand Blue and Gold which each have proper generic primary tokens.",
